# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CREDENTIALS MASTER FILE (single source of truth)
# Contains real private keys for live Google service accounts.
# All code reads from this file via googleDrive/credentials_loader.py
# (in-memory — no scattered .json files are generated anywhere).
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# googleDrive/credentials_master.json   <- already listed above (secrets!)

# Local UI overrides (e.g. uploader folder ID) — gitignored so each
# developer's local choice doesn't leak into the repo.
googleDrive/.upload_folder.json
